    <title>编译一个编译器</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>基于crosstool-ng编译一个aarch64架构的编译器。</p><h2 id="编译Cortex-a53-CPU的编译器"><a href="#编译Cortex-a53-CPU的编译器" class="headerlink" title="编译Cortex-a53 CPU的编译器"></a>编译Cortex-a53 CPU的编译器</h2><ol><li><h3 id="下载crosstools-ng源码"><a href="#下载crosstools-ng源码" class="headerlink" title="下载crosstools-ng源码"></a>下载crosstools-ng源码</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/crosstool-ng/crosstool-ng.git --depth=1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>直接下载仓库源码，<code>--depth=1</code> 下载深度为1，这样子容易下载好。</p></li><li><h3 id="安装相关依赖"><a href="#安装相关依赖" class="headerlink" title="安装相关依赖"></a>安装相关依赖</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">sudo apt install autoconf automake binutils bison flex makeinfo texinfo zip unzip<br>sudo apt install help2man libtool-bin ncurses-devel libncurses5-dev<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h3 id="编译安装crosstool-ng"><a href="#编译安装crosstool-ng" class="headerlink" title="编译安装crosstool-ng"></a>编译安装crosstool-ng</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-comment">#进入在源码目录</span><br>./bootstrap <br>./configure <br> make -j16<br> sudo make install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成后，执行如下命令进行测试。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ct-ng -v<br>GNU Make 4.2.1<br>Built for x86_64-pc-linux-gnu<br>Copyright (C) 1988-2016 Free Software Foundation, Inc.<br>License GPLv3+: GNU GPL version 3 or later &lt;http://gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html&gt;<br>This is free software: you are free to change and redistribute it.<br>There is NO WARRANTY, to the extent permitted by law.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h3 id="开始编译"><a href="#开始编译" class="headerlink" title="开始编译"></a>开始编译</h3><p>新建一个工作目录用来存放项目工程。</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> ~/project<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Crosstools-ng 提供了很多参考配置，如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ls samples <br>aarch64-ol7u9-linux-gnu<br>aarch64-rpi3-linux-gnu<br>aarch64-rpi4-linux-gnu<br>aarch64-unknown-linux-android<br>aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu<br>aarch64-unknown-linux-uclibc<br>alphaev56-unknown-linux-gnu<br>alphaev67-unknown-linux-gnu<br>.......<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制一个crosstool-ng中的sample配置文件，根据这个配置文件来修改。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ~/project<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> crosstool-ng/samples/aarch64-rpi3-linux-gnu/crosstool.config .config<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开始自定义配置：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd ~/project<br>ct-ng menuconfig<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.png" class="" title="编译器配置"><p>GCC版本修改：</p><img src="/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC.png" class="" title="编译器版本"><p>内核头修改：</p><img src="/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8%E5%A4%B4.png" class="" title="内核头"><p>名称（vendor）修改：</p><img src="/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png" class="" title="名称修改"><p>架构相关配置：</p><p>这里我们选择ARM\64位\A53\小端</p><img src="/2022/04/14/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8/%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84.png" class="" title="架构"><p>开始编译：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ct-ng build -j16<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译过程中会下载相关源码包，成果物会在路径：<code>~/x-tools</code> 下产生。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
